FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Find answers to common questions about our food delivery service
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: How does your food delivery app work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app connects you with local restaurants and delivery drivers. Simply browse menus, place your order, and track your food in real-time until it arrives at your doorstep.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Delivery fees vary depending on the restaurant's distance and current demand. The exact fee will be displayed before you confirm your order.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How long does delivery usually take?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Delivery times typically range from 30-45 minutes, but can vary based on the restaurant's preparation time, distance, and traffic conditions. You'll see an estimated delivery time before placing your order.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I schedule an order for later?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes! Our app allows you to schedule orders up to a week in advance. Simply select your desired delivery date and time during checkout.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: What if there's an issue with my order?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: If you encounter any problems with your order, please use the 'Help' section in the app to contact our customer support team. We're available 24/7 to assist you and ensure your satisfaction.
PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Food Delivery App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: How does the food delivery app work?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app connects you with local restaurants, allowing you to browse menus, place orders, and track your delivery in real-time. Simply select your dishes, pay through the app, and wait for your delicious meal to arrive at your doorstep.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: What are the delivery fees and estimated times?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Delivery fees vary depending on the restaurant and your location. Estimated delivery times are provided when you place your order, typically ranging from 30-60 minutes. You can track your order's progress in real-time through the app.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can I customize my order or leave special instructions?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! You can customize your order by adding special instructions or selecting available modifications for each dish. There's also a section for leaving notes for the restaurant or delivery driver.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: What if there's an issue with my order?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: If you experience any issues with your order, such as missing items or incorrect dishes, please use the 'Help' section in the app to report the problem. Our customer support team will assist you promptly to resolve the issue and ensure your satisfaction.
